<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Complete Your Video Uploads</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
    
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px;">
        <h2>Upload Reminder</h2>
    </div>
    
    <p>Hi <%= fName %>,</p>
    
    <p>It looks like your video upload for <strong><%= filename %></strong> was interrupted and hasn't finished yet.</p>
    
    <p>Please connect to a stable WiFi network and return to the application to resume your uploads.</p>
    
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 40px;">
        <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #777;">
            If you've already completed this step, please ignore this email.
        </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
